[
  {
    "text": "The snow is gray, where it is not red.",
    "start": 0.0,
    "end": 2.1
  },
  {
    "text": "Tanaka sits on the crater's edge and breathes.",
    "start": 2.94,
    "end": 5.06
  },
  {
    "text": "Each breath tastes of copper and burnt bone.",
    "start": 5.56,
    "end": 7.72
  },
  {
    "text": "Her ears ring at a frequency that has no name.",
    "start": 8.6,
    "end": 10.78
  },
  {
    "text": "She cannot hear Voss when he kneels beside her.",
    "start": 11.5,
    "end": 13.52
  },
  {
    "text": "She reads his lips.",
    "start": 14.16,
    "end": 14.9
  },
  {
    "text": "He is asking if she can feel his fingers.",
    "start": 15.66,
    "end": 17.16
  },
  {
    "text": "She can.",
    "start": 18.06,
    "end": 18.54
  },
  {
    "text": "Two.",
    "start": 19.4,
    "end": 19.7
  },
  {
    "text": "Then three.",
    "start": 20.38,
    "end": 20.98
  },
  {
    "text": "He nods.",
    "start": 21.7,
    "end": 22.3
  },
  {
    "text": "The hearing may return.",
    "start": 22.86,
    "end": 23.74
  },
  {
    "text": "May.",
    "start": 24.56,
    "end": 24.78
  },
  {
    "text": "She looks across the field.",
    "start": 25.58,
    "end": 26.7
  },
  {
    "text": "Neanderthal warriors lie where they fell.",
    "start": 27.34,
    "end": 29.22
  },
  {
    "text": "Their runes scars are dark.",
    "start": 29.76,
    "end": 30.98
  },
  {
    "text": "The bone armor is cracked open along every seam, spilling crystal and dust into the snow",
    "start": 31.74,
    "end": 35.64
  },
  {
    "text": "like salt.",
    "start": 35.64,
    "end": 36.08
  },
  {
    "text": "The blue glow that lit the battlefield minutes ago is gone.",
    "start": 36.96,
    "end": 39.44
  },
  {
    "text": "In its absence, the dust feels heavier.",
    "start": 40.22,
    "end": 42.1
  },
  {
    "text": "Closer.",
    "start": 42.84,
    "end": 43.28
  },
  {
    "text": "The rift still glows.",
    "start": 44.0,
    "end": 45.24
  },
  {
    "text": "Dimmer.",
    "start": 45.92,
    "end": 46.22
  },
  {
    "text": "Flickering.",
    "start": 47.04,
    "end": 47.34
  },
  {
    "text": "But present.",
    "start": 47.96,
    "end": 48.66
  },
  {
    "text": "Caglasts 30 meters from the crater.",
    "start": 49.64,
    "end": 51.18
  },
  {
    "text": "His massive chest rises and falls.",
    "start": 51.92,
    "end": 53.54
  },
  {
    "text": "Alive.",
    "start": 54.3,
    "end": 54.84
  },
  {
    "text": "His runes are dark, but his amber eyes are open.",
    "start": 54.84,
    "end": 57.76
  },
  {
    "text": "He stares at the sky.",
    "start": 58.54,
    "end": 59.46
  },
  {
    "text": "Tanaka stares at the rift.",
    "start": 60.26,
    "end": 61.32
  },
  {
    "text": "The pulse disrupted the anchoring spell.",
    "start": 61.96,
    "end": 63.52
  },
  {
    "text": "It did not destroy it.",
    "start": 64.08,
    "end": 65.06
  },
  {
    "text": "The door is damaged.",
    "start": 65.84,
    "end": 66.7
  },
  {
    "text": "It is not closed.",
    "start": 67.42,
    "end": 68.1
  },
  {
    "text": "She stands.",
    "start": 68.92,
    "end": 69.52
  },
  {
    "text": "Her legs tremble for two steps and then steady.",
    "start": 70.2,
    "end": 72.38
  },
  {
    "text": "She walks toward her command post.",
    "start": 73.14,
    "end": 74.54
  },
  {
    "text": "There will be a second engagement.",
    "start": 75.22,
    "end": 76.32
  },
  {
    "text": "There will be a third.",
    "start": 76.96,
    "end": 77.58
  },
  {
    "text": "She needs more emitters.",
    "start": 78.3,
    "end": 79.28
  },
  {
    "text": "She needs Voss to build them stronger.",
    "start": 79.54,
    "end": 81.06
  },
  {
    "text": "She needs the world to understand what is coming through that door.",
    "start": 81.06,
    "end": 84.02
  },
  {
    "text": "The snow crunches under her boots.",
    "start": 84.8,
    "end": 86.14
  },
  {
    "text": "Each step, a sentence in a language that dead cannot read.",
    "start": 86.76,
    "end": 89.1
  },
  {
    "text": "Behind her, the rift pulses once more.",
    "start": 89.78,
    "end": 91.7
  },
  {
    "text": "Then holds steady.",
    "start": 92.24,
    "end": 92.92
  },
  {
    "text": "The war is not over.",
    "start": 93.68,
    "end": 94.66
  },
  {
    "text": "The war has just begun.",
    "start": 95.24,
    "end": 96.28
  }
]